{
  "stem": "20142.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then they would just take a pistol, they said, you're of no use to us, and didn't even come to a close distance, but just shot him.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, several times.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And of course, you got scared, and you realized that you could be next.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Very unpleasant situation that you were living from day to day, and wondering what was better, to die or to be alive.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Somehow, many of us did not have the courage to take our own life by jumping on the wires of the separating one field from the other, which were loaded with a high voltage current.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were people who couldn't stand it and jumped on the wire.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were electrified-- electrocuted immediately.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the fun of it, the Germans said, was to engage other people to pull them off the wire.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the minute you touched it, you got the shock.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And some of us had learned that when they asked us to remove the body from the wires, we took our tunic off to protect our hands.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's how we pulled them off the wire.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Tunic.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The part of the uniform.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I did not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You-- you had-- you did not have any contact with the Russian POWs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were in separate barracks, and Polish Jews were in separate barracks, too.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the only thing that was on our mind, our course of conversation was food or dreaming about food.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Whatever we were getting was very, very precious to us, and what-- whatever we were getting was not enough for us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we knew that the days of our existence is coming to an end, because we could not exist under this condition for very long.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
